# Fixed, non-secret placeholder values for the test suite / CI only. These
# are never used against any real AWS account, vendor, or webhook — S3
# presigning is computed locally without a network call, and WebMock
# blocks any other outbound request the suite might otherwise attempt.
# Do not reuse these values anywhere outside the test environment.

